Package: brmsINLApower
Title: Bayesian Power Analysis with 'brms' and 'INLA'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Tony", "Myers",
           email = "admyers@aol.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4516-4829"))
Description: Tools for Bayesian power analysis and assurance 
    calculations using the 'brms' and 'INLA' frameworks. 
    Includes functions for simulation-based and analytical 
    approaches, sequential and two-stage designs, as well as 
    visualisation helpers for power curves, assurance, and 
    robustness analyses.
